<br>
A.  The Euphoric effects it has on the brain and body which could make a loaded person either dangerous behind the wheel, and/or dangerous out in public.<br>
<br>
B.  The long term detrimental effects associated with it.<br>
<br>
C.  Legalization would make it more accessible to minors--children, teens, etc.<br>
<br>
D.  Addiction &amp; overdose risks, as you mentioned.<br>
<br>
